summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 3E, page 39, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Greenwood Park 2nd Addition, Lots 27 and 28, Block 6, located two lots west of the northwest corner of 3rd Ave. N.W. and W. 80th St. as Neighborhood Business (BN) Zone.
